| Concern | Fix |
|---|---|
| Header fingerprinting | `app.disable('x-powered-by')` + `helmet()` |
| DoS via large bodies | `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` |
| Brute force / scraping | `express-rate-limit` with standard headers |
| Info leakage on errors | Central error middleware returns generic 500, logs detail server-side |
| Unvalidated params | `express-validator` with type coercion (`toInt()`) and bounds |
| Crash on unhandled rejection | `unhandledRejection` + `uncaughtException` handlers |
| Abrupt termination | `SIGTERM`/`SIGINT` graceful shutdown with force-exit fallback |
| IP spoofing behind proxy | `app.set('trust proxy', 1)` |
| Config in source | `process.env.PORT` |

