| DoS via large payloads | `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` + `express-rate-limit` |
| Missing security headers | `helmet()` sets CSP, HSTS, X-Frame-Options, etc. |
| Config hardcoded | `process.env.PORT` |
| Silent async crashes | `unhandledRejection` listener + `next(err)` in routes |
| No graceful shutdown | `SIGTERM`/`SIGINT` close the HTTP server cleanly |
| 404 not handled | Explicit 404 JSON response before error middleware |

