|---|---|
| Header leakage / XSS / clickjacking | `helmet()` + `x-powered-by` disabled |
| DoS via large bodies | `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` |
| Brute force / abuse | `express-rate-limit` |
| Injection via query/body | `express-validator` with strict types + `validate` middleware |
| Information disclosure in errors | Central error handler returns generic message; full error logged server-side |
| PII exposure | Strip email from default user response; require auth'd/scoped endpoint for full record |
| Crash on bad config | `process.env.PORT` with numeric coercion |
| Zombie processes on deploy | `SIGTERM`/`SIGINT` handlers + forced exit timeout |

