## 6. Logging & observability

`console.log` is not appropriate for production. Use a structured logger (e.g., `pino`) with request IDs so you can correlate errors without logging sensitive request bodies.

## 7. Graceful shutdown

On `SIGTERM`/`SIGINT`, close the server and drain in-flight requests before exiting — prevents dropped responses during deploys:
```js
