| Brute-force / DoS | `express-rate-limit` |
| Input tampering | Schema validation (zod/joi) on every route with a body/params |
| PII exposure | Remove emails from unauthenticated `/users`, add authz |
| Hardcoded port, no shutdown | `process.env.PORT` + `SIGTERM`/`SIGINT` handlers |
| `X-Powered-By` fingerprinting | `app.disable('x-powered-by')` (also done by helmet) |

